    subgraph Persistence
        DEV[(SQLite<br/>Dev)]
        PROD[(HANA Cloud<br/>Prod)]
    end

    BR -->|JWT scope: admin/editor/viewer| APR --> XSUAA
    AUTH -->|JWT scope: authority| APR
    CONS -->|no login| PUB

    APR --> DPP
